nce and they all sing the song. Then every previous cast member from the show joins them on stage, such as Jolene, Beverly, Rayna, Teddy, Luke, and more, revealing it is unscripted and [[breaking the fourth wall]] as creator Khouri thanks everyone for a wonderful six years and hopes they all have a life that's good. \n\n'''Songs:''' \"Free\" (sung by Juliette); \"Little Fire\" (sung by Maddie); \u201cDwell in my Soul\u201d (sung by Alannah); \u201cCarolina Rain\u201d (sung by Hallie); \u201cAll That Matters\u201d (sung by Jenny); \u201cHeart\u201d (sung by Daphne); \"A Life That's Good\" (sung by Rayna, Juliette, Deacon, Avery, Scarlett, Maddie, Daphne, Gunnar, and Will)\n| LineColor=#07282F\n}}\n}}</onlyinclude>\n\n==Ratings==\n===Nielsen===\n{{Television episode ratings\n| noshare   = y\n| title1   = [[#ep109|New Strings]]\n| date1    = January 4, 2018\n| rs1      = 0.2\n| viewers1 = 0.87<ref name=\"6.01\"/>\n| dvr1     = n/a\n| dvrv1    = n/a\n| total1   = n/a\n| totalv1  = n/a\n\n| title2   = [[#ep110|Second Chances]]\n| date2    = January 11, 2018\n| rs2      = 0.1\n| viewers2 = 0.78<ref name=\"6.02\"/>\n| dvr2     = 0.4\n| dvrv2    = 1.09\n| total2   = 0.5\n| totalv2  = 1.87<ref>{{cite web |url=http://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/dvr-ratings/cable-live-7-ratings-for-jan-8-14-2018/ |title='Nashville' grows by 400 percent in cable Live +7 ratings for Jan. 8-14 |last=Porter |first=Rick |date=January 26, 2018 |work=TV by the Numbers |accessdate=January 26, 2018}}</ref>\n\n| title3   = [[#ep111|Jump Then Fall]]\n| date3    = January 18, 2018\n| rs3      = 0.1\n| viewers3 = 0.73<ref name=\"6.03\"/>\n| dvr3     = 0.3\n| dvrv3    = 0.89\n| total3   = 0.4\n| totalv3  = 1.62<ref>{{cite web |url=http://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/dvr-ratings/cable-live-7-ratings-for-jan-15-21-2018/ |title='Assassination of Gianni Versace' posts solid gains in cable Live +7 ratings for Jan. 15-21 |last=Porter |first=Rick |date=February 1, 2018 |work=TV by the Numbers |accessdate=February 1, 20