 Up]]\n| date9    = June 7, 2018\n| rs9      = 0.2\n| viewers9 = 0.72<ref name=\"6.09\"/>\n| dvr9     = 0.2\n| dvrv9    = 0.95\n| total9   = 0.4\n| totalv9  = 1.67<ref>{{cite web|url=http://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/dvr-ratings/cloak-dagger-premiere-makes-good-gains-in-cable-live-7-ratings-for-june-4-10/|title='Cloak & Dagger' premiere makes good gains in cable Live +7 ratings for June 4\u201310|last=Porter|first=Rick|date=June 21, 2018|work=TV by the Numbers|accessdate=June 21, 2018}}</ref>\n\n| title10   = [[#ep118|Two Sparrows in a Hurricane]]\n| date10    = June 14, 2018\n| rs10      = 0.2\n| viewers10 = 0.76<ref name=\"6.10\"/>\n| dvr10     = n/a\n| dvrv10    = n/a\n| total10   = n/a\n| totalv10  = n/a\n\n| title11   = [[#ep119|No Place That Far]]\n| date11    = June 21, 2018\n| rs11      = 0.2\n| viewers11 = 0.75<ref name=\"6.11\"/>\n| dvr11     = 0.2\n| dvrv11    = 0.92\n| total11   = 0.4\n| totalv11  = 1.67<ref>{{cite web|url=https://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/dvr-ratings/cable-live-7-ratings-for-june-18-24-2018/|title='Yellowstone' premiere scores in cable Live +7 ratings for June 18\u201324|last=Porter|first=Rick|date=July 5, 2018|work=TV by the Numbers|accessdate=July 5, 2018}}</ref>\n\n| title12   = [[#ep120|The House That Built Me]]\n| date12    = June 28, 2018\n| rs12      = 0.1\n| viewers12 = 0.67<ref name=\"6.12\"/>\n| dvr12     = n/a\n| dvrv12    = n/a\n| total12   = n/a\n| totalv12  = n/a\n\n| title13   = [[#ep121|Strong Enough to Bend]]\n| date13    = July 5, 2018\n| rs13      = 0.1\n| viewers13 = 0.70<ref name=\"6.13\"/>\n| dvr13     = n/a\n| dvrv13    = n/a\n| total13   = n/a\n| totalv13  = n/a\n\n| title14   = [[#ep122|For the Sake of the Song]]\n| date14    = July 12, 2018\n| rs14      = 0.1\n| viewers14 = 0.62<ref name=\"6.14\"/>\n| dvr14     = 0.2\n| dvrv14    = 0.99\n| total14   = 0.3\n| totalv14  = 1.61<ref>{{cite web|url=https://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/dvr-ratings/cable-live-7-ratings-for-july-9-15-2018/|title='Yellowstone\u2019 and \u20